code: @SuppressWarnings("unchecked") @Test public void shouldCompareWithNullsLow() {     Comparator<String> c = NullSafeComparator.NULLS_LOW.     assertTrue(c.compare(null, "boo") < 0). }

@SuppressWarnings("unchecked") @Test public void shouldCompareWithNullsHigh() {     Comparator<String> c = NullSafeComparator.NULLS_HIGH.     assertTrue(c.compare(null, "boo") > 0).     assertTrue(c.compare(null, null) == 0). }
